@NODE "History" "History"
@TOC "MAIN"
@{b}History:@{ub}

    At the begining there was ExecPatch by Arthur Hagen, but it wasn't working properly with Executive and was causing some other problems, so I had no other choice and fixed the problem. I didn't bother to contact him (Arthur) due to fact that several other people reported that they couldn't contact him.

So, APatch was born...

* v0.1.0
    À fixed problem with Executive
        - Swith() was called in the wrong way...
    À fixed weird bug causing crashes
    À added exec.library patches:
        - Cause()
        - GetMsg()
        - ReplyMsg()
    À added a few speed improvements (who cares if it eats up 5k or 15k eh?)
    À a couple of 68000 instructions replaced with 68020+ ones
    À alligned the code

* v0.1.1
    À bug removed:
        - Dispatch() was patched twice!!!
            Changed font to size 15 in my editor ;-)
    À added graphics.library patches:
        - WaitBlit()
        - BltClear()
            Thanx to Mattias "Origo" Nilsson for the source code!!!
            Comparision:
            Original BltClr   : 14 seconds
            CpuBlit 3.100 & 4 : 7 seconds
            Origo's routine   : 5 seconds

* v0.1.2
    À improved Switch()
    À added exec.library patches:
        - CopyMem()
        - CopyMemQuick()

* v0.1.3
    À fixed bug I made in Signal() 
    À speedup in PutMsg() and ReplyMsg()
    À managed to speedup WaitBlit() 
    À fixed one silly alignment bug
    À added graphics.library patches: 
        - LockLayerRom()
        - UnlockLayerRom()
    À fixed another silly bug in Msg code (Cause() was called twice)

* v0.1.3Beta3 first public release (aminet)

* v0.1.3Beta4 
    À fixed a small problem in Dispatch()

* v0.1.3Beta5 (97.04.01)
    À bunch of stuff added and changed (too tired to point it out)
    À fixed problem with KS2.1 (ObtainSemaphore was patched...)
    À a few new functions added (Thanx to Dave Jones for the code!)

* v0.1.3Beta6 (97.04.06)
    À cleaned up some code, fixed alignment of a few loops
    À flushes cache when needed (hopefully)

* v0.1.3Beta6c (97.04.10)
    À d0 during int6 was trashed (fixed now) 
    À cleaned up int code
    À added graphics.library patch:
        - Draw() (not complete yet, but works great)
* v0.1.4 (97.04.26)
    À added WaitTOF()
    À WaitBlit() is even faster
    À Dispatch() improved
    À CopyMem routines changed
    À changed AutoInterrupt routines
    À patching routines improved
    À Switch() might cause some trouble on FPU equipped machines -fixed
    À BlackBorder patch added

* v0.2 Alpha (97.04.30)
    À Interrupts are even faster now...
    À caches & stuff fixed once again
    À minor changes

@ENDNODE
